ke: keep` in Lake shake.\n\nThe `headerStx?` parameter carries the header syntax used for checking trailing comments.\nWhen called from the Language Server, the main header syntax may have its trailing trivia\nstripped by `unsetTrailing` for caching purposes, so `origHeaderStx?` can supply the original\n(untrimmed) syntax to preserve `-- deprecated_module: ignore` annotations on the last import.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Import.html#Lean.Elab.checkDeprecatedImports","kind":"def","line":49,"name":"Lean.Elab.checkDeprecatedImports","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Import.lean#L49-L99"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Import.html#Lean.Elab.headerToImports\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">headerToImports</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">stx</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Import.html#Lean.Elab.HeaderSyntax\">HeaderSyntax</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">includeInit</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.true\">true</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Setup.html#Lean.Import\">Import</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Import.html#Lean.Elab.headerToImports","kind":"def","line":47,"name":"Lean.Elab.headerToImports","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Import.lean#L47-L47"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Import.html#Lean.Elab.Header